Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:24.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}張りつめた空気が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:30.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}高まる鼓動広がってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:36.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深く息吸い込んだなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:42.19,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう前しか見えないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:47.26,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰も代わる事出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:50.14,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私しか歩けない道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:53.18,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その涙も全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:56.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}輝きはじめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:02:00.97,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.03,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:09.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:13.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:16.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:21.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:23.48,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:28.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:24.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喜歡著緊張的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:30.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}興奮起來走向更廣闊的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:36.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深呼一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:42.19,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只專注於眼前的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:47.26,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰都無法替代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:50.14,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有我才能前進的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:53.18,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}連同那份淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:56.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全部開始閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:02:00.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因此將宿於手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.03,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}盡情揮揚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果斷地  徑直地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:09.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向著明天全力進發
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:13.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在轉瞬即逝之間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:16.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}實現那夢中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}無論它多麼虛幻和遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:21.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也絕不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:23.48,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和僅屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:28.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}竹劍節奏響徹永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久沒有進行晨練了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一直在參加部團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就是大賽了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以往一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好  已經全部康復了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:00:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:41.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第22話\N敗者與勝者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！面！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近真有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本週末就是關東大賽了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是很了不起的大賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關東地區的水平和中國地區完全不是一個層次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能在上面取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們部的強勁也自然能成為焦點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一定能讓他收回解雇的成名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說我可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有小珠的呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手有效
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都…從小聰莉那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下了一本！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很精彩！宮崎同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強哦  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續！聰莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁我還沒有忘記剛才的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不能輸呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定行！這次一定行啊！老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是嗎  那就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  勇次君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼  繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關東大賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真讓人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠最近變強了  更重要的是變精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  果然參加部團活動是對的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說  和同齡人一起練習是一件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  在這個時候  布雷巴出現…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小珠救了出來對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都記住啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…鈴木同學也會參加關東大賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  這次的大賽對大家來說會是一個大活動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得太有部團的感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而會讓人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好比「如果只有我輸了怎麼辦呢」之類
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊  勇次君很強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣明天就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢  這才開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後啊  段君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不碰遙控器一個小時就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個週末就是大賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦死了  誰會去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們早就不參加社團活動了  拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大賽前我先這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們蠻強的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說「蠻」…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說的話你就下個定論嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能下定論的只有小珠一個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果覺得自己「蠻強」就自滿起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉眼就會被別人追過去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這麼說  我怎麼覺得他兩眼就盯著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說…那個嘛  不能粗心大意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有幹勁的話一定會輸掉比賽的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣都會輸嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要我怎麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  換人換人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉紅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綠色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級勇次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎長官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我是黃色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是室江高劍道部的證明哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是部長！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  這就是勝利的吉祥物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高！Fight！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真緊張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次參加這樣氣氛的大賽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和以前的比賽是絕對不一樣的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在這裡打贏才是真材實料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是還用那種迴轉壽司打發我可絕對說不過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迴轉壽司？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:08:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:08:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  你們來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次合宿後就沒見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我們可是絕好狀態哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你切什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看過出賽表了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要碰面的話就在決賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的團體戰  要決勝負就在那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是大家都能贏到決賽才行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少說什麼不明不白的話  你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將！在這裡別這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們參加多少比賽？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團體戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不贏四場是不能到決賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種程度對現在的我們來說輕而易舉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決戰  在明天的個人戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種熱血…讓人想起了過去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在決勝戰碰面吧  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目標也是那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會再贏一次的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然練習劍道的人逐漸減少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但充滿熱情的諸位仍然聚集在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個退居二線的人感到非常欣慰並對你們充滿期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}凜就在這些人裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至可以說在你們其中將會出現把全新的劍道推向社會的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在第五十五會關東高中生劍道大賽開賽！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…貓貓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道之神…是存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第幾個出場？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次峰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  今天就做個了斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是還覺得她是以前的宮崎同學  小心吃苦頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不好意思  我也不是以前的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無法超越我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過二刀流在高中生正式戰不能用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼想的呢  凱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹有效
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！小聰莉做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你有什麼招數
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～趕上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都幫你拍下來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效  比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  一勝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一把刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這樣就出現可能性了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之是一刀嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來  上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是二刀流很複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我輸在這裡  就沒有練劍道的意義了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退開！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮崎同學！好好注意前方！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個白癡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用二刀流的話  一刀又怎麼會弱？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都！加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但仍不及我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹有效
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜呢  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一點就能贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說  都是輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不甘心…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要贏哦  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三回戰出線啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她們是真的想和你們打嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是場好比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎歡迎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經把小都都的份一起彌補完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠和東就不用說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果紀梨乃和小鞘能贏的話  就真的能進決戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你光這麼一廂情願地想的話  小心摔了跟頭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看對戰表了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下來就輪到我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜是秀玉高的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大將
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我這麼說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴是贏不過施奈德的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼贏不過的原因  我今天就告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠？你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個…我認識的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒錢啦  走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再殺會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啥  白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡你做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？這傢伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火了？不就是個遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們夠了  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用他們續幣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒雖然贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但次鋒和中堅都敗下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦戰中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像沒什麼精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個次峰基本上都不帶動的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:17:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像室江高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她做大將的話  沒可能輸的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃！拜託了！給小珠個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  來加油吧  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下局小都都也會復活的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要贏！拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手有效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶！贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子下來就有機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就拜託囉  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～真險吶  對方好強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  畢竟接下來是小珠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下局換下次序好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓宮崎同學做前鋒比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙開始動搖了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等比賽結束後說說她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上段？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個時候一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會輸？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  振作！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在比賽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單手面？從上段？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還拿下了一本…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人…好強！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那是弱點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  安藤同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好沒那個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要拿下一局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠！不錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.39,0:20:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要贏！我要贏！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是正義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  會輸就是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是正義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要拿下一局  拿下一局
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要贏…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以對她用…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白方  秀玉高獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:22.62,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:27.64,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:34.03,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:55.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:23:02.12,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:09.99,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:17.33,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:20.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.33,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:32.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.33,0:23:35.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:40.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:47.85,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:22.62,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:27.64,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中閃耀著的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:34.03,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:55.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗邊光著腳丫  仰望著夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:23:02.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有無法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:09.99,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮現出午時的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:17.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒勞得令人著急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:20.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}閉上眼睛傾聽心中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:32.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然無法得知  它想與我相見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.33,0:23:35.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:40.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光輝而耀眼的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:47.85,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.63,0:23:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小島田禮美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.34,0:23:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然今天小都輸掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.38,0:23:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但消沉的小都對禮美來說也一樣OK
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥氣的小都  兇暴的小都  微笑的小都
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發怒的小都  睡著的小都
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.72,0:24:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳尖踢到了衣櫃角跳起來的小都
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.56,0:24:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪個都無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.82,0:24:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回「謊言與沉默」會看到什麼樣的小都呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.01,0:24:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～只是想像的話就…（噴）
